I'm sitting here eyes full of tears 😭 trying to figure out what i'm supposed to do now!!! It hurts so much knowing that you gave me this gift and, i feel like i’m failing at it and on you. The little  boy in me is tired and broken and i never get to heal him. He is full of patches where i have been trying to fix him!!! HELP US PLEASE HE CAN'T TAKE NO MORE AND IM OUT OF EASY FIX!! I have been hiding behind this smile and personality that isn't starting to hurt 😞. I'm not lucky 🍀 with love ❤️ and life and it getting to me. The boy in me is tired of entertaining people and making them feel good then getting left behind. I poured myself into my work just to be disregarded like trash 🚮 on the street. Then given a half ass excuse, so i'm angry 😡. I'm  going to trust you but my faith is hanging on my a thread. I JUST WANT SOME PEACE FOR MY HEART AND MIND PLEASE, DO IT FOR ME!!!
